_sText:
Counter-Strike: Source Beta 2004's files repackaged to work with the current game.
Files taken from hl2-beta.ru : Counter-Strike: Source Beta (2004)

I do not own any of these files. 
Only renamed a few files to work with the current build of CS:S

Key features:
1) Old HUD
2) CS 1.6 Icons for weapons and random character select
3) Old weapon models. textures, sounds and animations
4) Old CT and T models (simple renaming of the files to replace the 8 selectable models)

NOTE: Not everything will work as intended, so please keep that in mind.
The only observable bug is the M4A1 silenced w_ model when held in hand of a player is invisible in thirdperson.
